<div class="ArticleView">
        <a href="/en/dep/fad/Selected-topics/Sami-policy/sami-languages/the-use-of-the-sami-language-in-the-publ.html?id=86942">
            <img src="/upload/AID/temabilder/sami/tema_sami_forvaltning100x75.jpg" alt="Samepolitikk
Author: Kenneth Hætta" class="ArticleImg" />
        </a>
        
        <div class="ArticleImgContent">
            <h2><a href="/en/dep/fad/Selected-topics/Sami-policy/sami-languages/the-use-of-the-sami-language-in-the-publ.html?id=86942">The use of the Sámi language in the public administration</a></h2>        
                
            <p>
               Active and wider use of the Sámi language is a very important element in the further development of Sámi culture. Similarly, it is also important that the Sámi language is used in the public context. 
            </p>
            
